- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as TensorFlow is a popular framework for machine learning and the paper proposes heuristic strategies to optimize its performance. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category for the same reason as cs.AI. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with optimizing the performance of a complex system (TensorFlow) on heterogeneous devices. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes heuristic strategies for optimizing the execution of a graph-based program (TensorFlow).
